    <title>Viewing objects</title>
    <shortdesc>How you view files in CWRC depends on the file itself. XML documents are viewed in
        the visualization tool CWRC-Writer. Image, audio, video, and document files open within your
        browser. For more information see <b>Content Models Reference</b>.</shortdesc>
